Wheeljack-X/Empath::

Wheeljack looks at the newcomers.  "Hi folks.  I'm Wheeljack-X, 
mechanic, inventor and all-around nutbar."

Empath sighs and transforms to robot mode, showing off the Decepticon 
insignia on her wings.  She offers an arm to support Windlord.  "Why 
is it we can never get any time to ourselves anymore?"
